### Health check style startup probe
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/bases

### 1. Create a knowledge base
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/bases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "knowledgeBaseName": "企业客服知识库",
  "description": "用于测试退款、发票、售后问答"
}

### 2. List knowledge bases
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/bases

### 3. Upload a document to a knowledge base
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/documents/upload?knowledgeBaseId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="faq.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

# 退款规则
订单支付后7天内可申请退款。

# 发票规则
企业用户可申请增值税专用发票。
--WebAppBoundary--

### 4. List documents under a knowledge base
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/documents?knowledgeBaseId=1

### 5. Preview document chunks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/documents/1/chunks

### 6. Rebuild document index
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/documents/1/rebuild-index

### 7. Create a chat session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "sessionName": "聊天"
}

### 8. List sessions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/sessions?userId=1

### 8.1 Rename session
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/chat/sessions/1/name
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionName": "公积金可支付费用"
}

### 8.2 Toggle pin session
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/chat/sessions/1/pin

### 9. Stream chat with knowledge base filtering
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "userId": 1,
  "sessionId": 1,
  "knowledgeBaseId": 1,
  "question": "退款流程是什么？"
}

### 10. Query message history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/sessions/1/messages?userId=1
